setPopulate(boolean) - Method in class com.iontrading.mkv.MkvEntitlements.Query
Decide if the query should populate the local cache or not
The API keeps all the results of Entitlement Server queries into an internal cache
Calls to the MkvEntitlementManager.eval(com.iontrading.mkv.MkvEntitlementRequest, com.iontrading.mkv.events.MkvEntitlementRequestEvalListener): first check if the result is present inside the cache: if so, the remote call to the Entitlement Server is not performed
When any update occurs on the Entitlement Server side, the internal cache is invalidated
